his impressive recipe produces a two-course chicken dinner in under two hours. First, a tasty butternut squash soup cooks as a whole chicken steams in the Varoma, guaranteeing incredibly tender and moist meat. Steamed fresh vegetables and a flavourful red wine gravy complete the main course, resulting in a delicious and simple dinner for six."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","2h","6 portions"]}